          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "I've been using Namecheap across multiple projects for years — side blogs, client sites, small e-commerce stores — and the value keeps impressing me. It's not the flashiest name in the industry, but it delivers where it counts: low prices, zero hidden fees, and a user experience that doesn't require a CS degree.",
